-- S.Africa's Alexander Forbes surges above IPO price
-- By David Dolan and Tiisetso Motsoeneng
-- Thu Jul 24, 2014 03:09AM EDT
-- None



JOHANNESBURG, July 24 (Reuters) - Shares in Alexander Forbes <AFHJ.J> surged 8 percent above their IPO price on Thursday as the pension fund manager returned to the Johannesburg bourse in South Africa's biggest share floatation in four years.

